content.rendered:
Directed by K.S. Ravindra

Written by Srikanth Vissa. K.S. Ravindra. K.S. Ravindra. Kona Venkat. K. Chakravarthy Reddy

Cast Raashi Khanna (Harika). Prakash Raj (Vijay Prakash). Naga Chaitanya Akkineni (V. Karthik Shivaram). Kishore Kumar G.(Anwar Sadat). Payal Rajput (Vennela). Venkatesh Daggubati (Venkatarathnam Naidu). Nassar (Ramanarayana). Rao Ramesh (Pasupathi). Raghu Babu (Happy Hanumantha Rao). Geetha (Lakshmi). Hyper Aadi (Karthik’s Friend). Vidyullekha Raman (Candy). Pooja Ramachandran (A Bride). Mamilla Shailaja Priya (Harika’s Mother). Adithya Menon (Ajay Ahuja). Chammak Chandra (Nukaraju). Charu Haasan (Namboothiri). Nagineedu (Karthik’s Paternal Grandfather). Narra Srinivas (Rama Rao). C.V.L. Narasimha Rao (Master). Arun Kumar Dasari (Dora Babu).Raghu Kumar Karumanchi. Bhanu Prakash (Student). Gundu Sudharshan (School Teacher). Sivannarayana (Vennela’s Father). Siddharth Gollapudi (Fighter Pilot). Shivakarthik ((as Shiva)). Indu Anand (Karthik’s Paternal Grandmother). Ak (Goon). Master Naga Mahesh (Vennela’s student). Jeeva (Babji)

Languages Telugu

Producers D. Suresh Babu. Danish Khan. Sujith Kumar Kolli. Vivek Kuchibhotla. T.G. Vishwa Prasad. Vijaya Rajesh

Production People Media Factor. Suresh Production
